<p>Increase your content velocity when:</p>
<ul>
<li>Organic traffic is growing 15%+ per quarter (the system is working, scale it)</li>
<li>You have covered your primary keyword clusters (expand to adjacent topics)</li>
<li>Competitor analysis shows they are outpublishing you</li>
<li>You have budget headroom and want to accelerate growth</li>
</ul>
<h3>When to Decrease Velocity</h3>
